1
00:00:38,820 --> 00:00:40,820
=Visage and Soul=

2
00:00:40,820 --> 00:00:43,040
("The Unique Her"
Trilogy on Women's Relationships)

3
00:00:44,720 --> 00:00:47,640
=Episode 14=

4
00:01:13,040 --> 00:01:15,800
The human body is a tiny universe.

5
00:01:16,640 --> 00:01:19,000
Its meridians are like the stars.

6
00:01:55,800 --> 00:01:59,200
Hegu acupoint. It helps relax muscles,
improves circulation,

7
00:01:59,200 --> 00:02:00,920
and reduce fever and pain.

8
00:02:02,760 --> 00:02:03,800
Hegu acupoint?

9
00:02:06,520 --> 00:02:07,040
That's right.

10
00:02:08,200 --> 00:02:09,160
Hegu.

11
00:02:31,800 --> 00:02:32,800
Don't worry.

12
00:02:32,800 --> 00:02:33,920
I sterilized it.

13
00:02:42,840 --> 00:02:43,800
You have a fever?

14
00:02:46,200 --> 00:02:48,360
Don't paint in a draft anymore.

15
00:02:48,360 --> 00:02:49,240
You'll catch a cold.

16
00:02:59,880 --> 00:03:01,080
W-What are you doing?

17
00:03:01,880 --> 00:03:03,720
I'm going to give you a
few acupuncture needles.

18
00:03:03,720 --> 00:03:04,520
It'll bring your fever down faster.

19
00:03:05,320 --> 00:03:06,680
Relax. It won't hurt.

20
00:03:07,040 --> 00:03:08,040
I sterilized everything.

21
00:03:33,680 --> 00:03:34,640
You're awake.

22
00:03:35,920 --> 00:03:37,120
How are you feeling?

23
00:03:39,040 --> 00:03:40,600
I'm fine now.

24
00:03:41,360 --> 00:03:42,160
That's good.

25
00:03:43,640 --> 00:03:44,320
By the way,

26
00:03:44,720 --> 00:03:45,480
let me ask you something.

27
00:03:46,200 --> 00:03:47,560
Did I ever study acupuncture?

28
00:03:56,800 --> 00:03:57,920
Why would you ask that?

29
00:04:00,040 --> 00:04:02,200
You have no idea
how scary last night was.

30
00:04:02,600 --> 00:04:04,080
All the medicine
in your house had expired.

31
00:04:04,440 --> 00:04:05,680
And you refused to go to the hospital.

32
00:04:08,240 --> 00:04:09,320
So I had no choice

33
00:04:10,120 --> 00:04:11,560
but to give it a try.

34
00:04:13,560 --> 00:04:14,960
What exactly did you do to me?

35
00:04:17,160 --> 00:04:19,160
I don't even know
what I was thinking then.

36
00:04:19,160 --> 00:04:21,360
I just felt like those
were the right spots.

37
00:04:22,360 --> 00:04:23,960
So I just did it.

38
00:04:24,400 --> 00:04:26,280
Y-You actually went through with it?

39
00:04:28,200 --> 00:04:29,520
What if you'd hit the wrong spot?

40
00:04:29,520 --> 00:04:30,960
What if you'd killed me?

41
00:04:31,400 --> 00:04:32,640
But you're not dead, are you?

42
00:04:33,360 --> 00:04:35,200
And you do feel better, right?

43
00:04:37,840 --> 00:04:39,200
Don't change the subject.

44
00:04:39,200 --> 00:04:39,920
Did I study it or not?

45
00:04:39,920 --> 00:04:41,080
I'm telling you,

46
00:04:41,080 --> 00:04:42,600
You just got lucky this time.

47
00:04:44,040 --> 00:04:45,320
Good thing I'm tough.

48
00:04:50,600 --> 00:04:52,200
(How does she know acupuncture?)

49
00:04:52,200 --> 00:04:53,520
(Did she actually study it)

50
00:04:53,520 --> 00:04:54,720
(or was it just a coincidence?)

51
00:05:15,440 --> 00:05:16,720
I just got over being sick.

52
00:05:17,080 --> 00:05:18,440
I let you stick needles in me,

53
00:05:18,440 --> 00:05:19,560
and this is what you're feeding me?

54
00:05:22,440 --> 00:05:23,560
Who said it's for you?

55
00:05:29,960 --> 00:05:31,320
Just kidding.

56
00:05:31,680 --> 00:05:32,640
Go ahead and eat.

57
00:05:39,600 --> 00:05:40,560
Want a bite?

58
00:05:40,560 --> 00:05:41,520
You eat first.

59
00:05:44,680 --> 00:05:46,240
One sausage is too much for me.

60
00:05:46,240 --> 00:05:47,240
Let's split it.

61
00:05:52,600 --> 00:05:54,600
One sausage is too much for me.

62
00:05:56,600 --> 00:05:57,760
Let's split it.

63
00:06:02,680 --> 00:06:03,720
What are you daydreaming about?

64
00:06:03,720 --> 00:06:04,600
Eat up.

65
00:06:13,120 --> 00:06:15,080
Qiao Zhiwei didn't
get his way this time.

66
00:06:15,360 --> 00:06:16,520
The way he is,

67
00:06:16,520 --> 00:06:18,080
he won't let this go.

68
00:06:21,160 --> 00:06:22,280
He must've had help

69
00:06:22,680 --> 00:06:23,720
switching that painting.

70
00:06:24,320 --> 00:06:26,080
You need to be extra
careful from now on.

71
00:06:30,040 --> 00:06:32,120
Actually, that's what
I wanted to discuss.

72
00:06:34,520 --> 00:06:36,120
I'd like you to help manage the gallery.

73
00:06:39,120 --> 00:06:41,480
I honestly don't know much
about art right now.

74
00:06:42,200 --> 00:06:43,760
I got lucky this time.

75
00:06:44,120 --> 00:06:46,360
Next time, I might not be so lucky.

76
00:06:47,120 --> 00:06:48,440
But you know a lot.

77
00:06:48,440 --> 00:06:49,600
You know a whole lot.

78
00:06:49,600 --> 00:06:50,000
So...

79
00:06:50,000 --> 00:06:51,000
So

80
00:06:51,480 --> 00:06:53,440
what exactly would my role
be at the gallery?

81
00:06:55,040 --> 00:06:56,480
As your fiancé?

82
00:06:56,480 --> 00:06:57,360
Or...

83
00:06:58,680 --> 00:06:59,880
Can you be serious for once?

84
00:06:59,880 --> 00:07:00,960
I am serious.

85
00:07:01,680 --> 00:07:03,440
I don't do things without a title.

86
00:07:06,760 --> 00:07:08,760
Haven't you always
called yourself my fiancé?

87
00:07:17,360 --> 00:07:18,800
Fiancé.

88
00:07:29,040 --> 00:07:30,200
Xiaoyi, from now on,

89
00:07:30,200 --> 00:07:31,640
Mr. Qin will be in charge here.

90
00:07:31,640 --> 00:07:33,400
If anything comes up,
just go to him directly.

91
00:07:33,800 --> 00:07:35,640
Then, Xiaomi, things
will be much easier for you.

92
00:07:38,000 --> 00:07:39,160
She'll be busy managing me.

93
00:07:40,120 --> 00:07:42,120
The gallery feels a little
too romantic today.

94
00:07:43,320 --> 00:07:44,880
I'll go make coffee for you two.

95
00:07:45,320 --> 00:07:46,680
Make him a caramel latte.

96
00:07:47,080 --> 00:07:48,480
Got it, Miss Qiao.

97
00:07:57,280 --> 00:07:58,600
Honestly, I feel torn.

98
00:08:02,480 --> 00:08:03,600
I've always

99
00:08:04,200 --> 00:08:06,720
wanted to protect everything
my father left behind.

100
00:08:07,960 --> 00:08:10,040
That's why I've worked
so hard at painting.

101
00:08:10,960 --> 00:08:12,280
But I've realized

102
00:08:13,640 --> 00:08:16,160
I don't love it as much as people think.

103
00:08:25,480 --> 00:08:26,840
Honestly, I'm afraid.

104
00:08:29,680 --> 00:08:30,920
I'm afraid that if
I remember everything,

105
00:08:32,680 --> 00:08:34,360
and it's better
not to remember at all.

106
00:08:46,520 --> 00:08:48,040
Didn't I tell you to leave it to me?

107
00:08:49,360 --> 00:08:50,640
If you don't feel like
coming here anymore,

108
00:08:51,160 --> 00:08:52,280
then don't.

109
00:09:08,080 --> 00:09:09,080
That plan

110
00:09:09,080 --> 00:09:10,200
actually sounds like a solid plan.

111
00:09:10,480 --> 00:09:11,280
However,

112
00:09:13,920 --> 00:09:16,080
you've been distracted all day.

113
00:09:16,080 --> 00:09:17,520
Is something on your mind?

114
00:09:22,200 --> 00:09:22,840
No.

115
00:09:24,680 --> 00:09:26,440
I've just had a lot on my mind lately.

116
00:09:29,000 --> 00:09:30,320
It's because of Qiao Xiaomi, isn't it?

117
00:09:31,920 --> 00:09:33,040
How about this?

118
00:09:33,040 --> 00:09:34,680
Let me do a hypnosis session for you.

119
00:09:35,240 --> 00:09:36,400
Maybe

120
00:09:36,400 --> 00:09:38,160
it might help clear your mind.

121
00:09:45,080 --> 00:09:46,000
Relax.

122
00:09:46,480 --> 00:09:47,760
You're safe here.

123
00:09:55,880 --> 00:09:56,640
Lie down.

124
00:10:04,280 --> 00:10:05,440
Relax.

125
00:10:05,840 --> 00:10:07,000
Take a deep breath.

126
00:10:08,000 --> 00:10:09,360
Close your eyes.

127
00:10:11,360 --> 00:10:12,320
Relax.

128
00:10:12,840 --> 00:10:13,880
Take a deep breath.

129
00:10:14,800 --> 00:10:16,000
Close your eyes.

130
00:10:46,848 --> 00:10:48,918
♪We say good morning, we say good night♪

131
00:10:48,918 --> 00:10:52,338
♪We say we miss each other,
but never speak of the hurt♪

132
00:10:53,938 --> 00:10:55,828
♪The sweeter it is, the luckier we seem♪

133
00:10:55,828 --> 00:10:59,818
♪Yet the more romantic,
the rougher the road♪

134
00:11:01,058 --> 00:11:02,918
♪Let me go, set me free♪

135
00:11:02,918 --> 00:11:06,958
♪Let me drown in reckless silence♪

136
00:11:07,498 --> 00:11:12,908
♪We were perfect for each other,
yet you never admitted it♪

137
00:11:14,258 --> 00:11:16,398
♪The freedom you gave me♪

138
00:11:16,398 --> 00:11:20,038
♪Became the heaviest chain I bear♪

139
00:11:21,298 --> 00:11:23,568
♪Love can barely move forward♪

140
00:11:23,568 --> 00:11:27,348
♪Yet the words still linger unspoken♪

141
00:11:28,448 --> 00:11:30,688
♪The closeness I long for♪

142
00:11:30,688 --> 00:11:35,078
♪There's no need for you
to keep avoiding it♪

143
00:11:35,488 --> 00:11:37,308
♪I don't want to break free♪

144
00:11:37,308 --> 00:11:42,678
♪Take back the chains
disguised as freedom♪
